{"title":"走掉的花店","date":"2020-08-07T14:00:14.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Aug 7, 2020","L":"08/07/2020","MM-DD":"08-07"},"author":"Birch","thumbnail":"https://cdn.wardzhou.art/img/flower-shop-3800566_6401.webp","link":"2020/08/07/GoneTheFlowerShop","comments":true,"tags":["诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2020-12-14T15:10:11.493Z","content":"<p>附近新开了家花店<br>\n很小的一间屋子<br>\n装不下的花溢到门前</p>\n<p>每天路过都会瞥一眼<br>\n花店里只有一个姑娘<br>\n有时是在打理着花<br>\n有时只是坐在那望着外面</p>\n<p>我想，什么时候会收到一束<br>\n从这家店里买来的花呢？</p>\n<p>后来过了很久<br>\n花店和那姑娘不见了<br>\n空荡荡的房子似乎<br>\n宽敞得空洞<br>\n新挂上去的牌子<br>\n毫不讨喜</p>\n<p>我想，我大概也不需要一束<br>\n来自那花店里的花吧</p>\n","prev":{"title":"Retrospection","link":"2020/08/14/Retrospection"},"next":{"title":"Door","link":"2020/08/01/Door"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2020/08/07/GoneTheFlowerShop/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Birch","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"December 14, 2020"},"reading_time":"141 words in 1 min"}